00:00:28.065 --> 00:00:29.500 align:middle line:90%
I certainly am.

00:00:29.500 --> 00:00:30.890 align:middle line:90%
It's just come out.

00:00:30.890 --> 00:00:31.660 align:middle line:90%
Exciting.

